OL,3,CCalls for hate crime legislation as
OL,4,CLGBTQ+ assaults increase
OL,6,FThe number of hate crimes against
OL,7,FLGBTQ+ people in Jersey is on the
OL,8,Frise, according to figures from States
OL,9,Fof Jersey Police.
OL,11,FIn 2024 there were 10 incidents,
OL,12,Fcompared to 2 the previous year, with
OL,13,Fthe the majority being physical
OL,14,Fassaults.
OL,16,FIt's prompted calls from campaigners
OL,17,Ffor hate crime legislation to be
OL,18,Fimplemented in Jersey.
