OL,3,CCalls for hate crime legislation as
OL,4,CLGBTQ+ assaults increase
OL,6,FHate crime, typically one involving
OL,7,Fviolence, that is motivated by
OL,8,Fprejudice on the basis of ethnicity,
OL,9,Freligion, sexual orientation, or
OL,10,Fsimilar grounds.
OL,12,FIn reaction to the figures, Deputy
OL,13,FLouise Doublet, said "I'm disappointed
OL,14,Fbut I'm not surprised.
OL,16,F"Although we sometimes assume that
OL,17,Fprogress is linear and we're getting
OL,18,Fmore progressive, what we're seeing is
OL,19,Fan increase in negative rhetoric
OL,20,Fagainst the LGBTQI+ community.
