OL,3,CCalls for hate crime legislation as
OL,4,CLGBTQ+ assaults increase
OL,6,F"We need to challenge bad behaviour
OL,7,Fwhere it occurs, we should not stand
OL,8,Ffor any violence or intolerance or
OL,9,Fhatred towards our community.
OL,11,F"We need hate crime legislation, that
OL,12,Fsends a message then that this is
OL,13,Fcompletely unacceptable."
OL,15,FKaye Nicholson, CEO of Liberate Jersey
OL,16,Fsaid LGBTQ hate crimes remain
OL,17,Fsignificantly underreported.
OL,19,F"In Jersey I would expect that's
OL,20,Fpartly to do with the fact that
OL,21,Fthere's no hate crime legislation.
